===A new fashion trend...===
{{Messages|text=
:'''Aglaea:''' A new fashion trend has swept through Okhema
:'''Aglaea:''' Youngsters would occasionally mimic the legendary heroes of Amphoreus by dressing in similar outfits and gathering at the plaza
:'''Aglaea:''' Lately, I've seen many take inspiration from your group's attire
:{Choice} That's called cosplay
::'''(Trailblazer):''' It's all part of costume play
::'''Aglaea:''' You seem to know a lot about this
:{Choice} How dare they wear my clothes
::'''(Trailblazer):''' How dare they wear my clothes without me knowing?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' This is copyrighted!
::'''(Trailblazer):''' [[File:Sticker PPG 07 Pom-Pom 08.png|80px]]
::'''Aglaea:''' Your arrival has made an indelible impression on the people of Okhema
:{Choice} I'll join too!
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I'll join in too! I'll play as myself
::'''(Trailblazer):''' [[File:Sticker PPG 07 Pom-Pom 01.png|80px]]
::'''Aglaea:''' The residents of Okhema would certainly appreciate it
:'''Aglaea:''' It's probably a professional quirk, but your outfits really caught my eye when we first met
:'''Aglaea:''' The tailoring is sculptural, with a distinctly architectural aesthetic
:'''Aglaea:''' The stitching is diverse, with some techniques that are unfamiliar even to me
:'''Aglaea:''' The bold, yet tasteful choice of colors matches well with each of your individual qualities
:'''Aglaea:''' It gives me, as a dressmaster, a lot of new inspiration
:'''Aglaea:''' If you'd like, I can recommend some local outfits for you
:{Choice} What do you think would suit me?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' What do you think would suit me?
::'''Aglaea:''' Let me think about it
::'''Aglaea:''' Perhaps a black hooded cloak &mdash; it's a timeless classic
:{Choice} How about something a true hero would wear!
::'''(Trailblazer):''' How about something a true hero would wear!
::'''Aglaea:''' Haha, aren't you already wearing one?
:{Choice} I'd love to try on your dress
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I'd love to try on something like yours &mdash; I like it
::'''(Trailblazer):''' [[File:Sticker PPG 07 Pom-Pom 06.png|80px]]
::'''Aglaea:''' Clothing should be tailored to fit &mdash; everyone has their own style
::'''Aglaea:''' These days, I lean toward simple and elegant outfits, but I can customize them to suit your preferences
:'''Aglaea:''' I once had a passion for collecting beautiful garments and even had a wardrobe as large as a house
:'''Aglaea:''' However, I now hope that clothes are available to anyone who needs them, rather than solely belonging to me
:'''Aglaea:''' {{tx|Missing sticker}}{{subst:void|<!--SpriteOutput/Emoji/120007.png-->}}
}}
